org.jivesoftware.smackx.jingle.mediaimpl.jspeex

Class SpeexMediaManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jivesoftware.smackx.jingle.media.JingleMediaManager
      • org.jivesoftware.smackx.jingle.mediaimpl.jspeex.SpeexMediaManager

  • public class SpeexMediaManager
extends JingleMediaManager
    Implements a jingleMediaManager using JMF based API and JSpeex. It supports Speex codec. This API only currently works on windows.
